data.description: Move-in ready 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home in Athens featuring just over 2,000 finished sq ft with a rare, detached 4-car garage (26'X62') - plenty of space for vehicle storage, boats, campers, you name it, w/ concrete floor & included garage wood stove & corner bar/desk. Private backyard with neighboring farm field views! Inside features a spacious entry with a main level laundry room / mudroom (front-load washer & dryer included). Functional kitchen with quality Amish-made cabinetry and included stainless kitchen appliances (only a few years old). Spacious formal dining room with beautiful hardwood flooring and patio door to the front deck, with the living room just around the corner. Modern paint colors & fixtures throughout giving the home a contemporary look. Huge main level full bath with tons of storage space (double door closet w/ another built-in cabinet) and dual sink vanity.,Upstairs features 3 bedrooms - one of which is a spacious 20'X11' room with closet and attic storage access. The finished basement offers more space for a rec room with beautiful flooring, a modern half bath, and 4th bedroom suite w/ a walk-in closet and large built-in office area. Great for a home office or work from home set up! Extra storage beneath the staircase and in the unfinished utility room. Additional updates include the roof shingles (approx. 2015) - extra shingles in the garage are included, 200 AMP electrical panel, and an efficient tankless water heater. Great location, walking distance from Athens County Park, and local conveniences. Centrally located - just over 30 minutes from Merrill & Wausau and approx. 20 mins from Abbotsford. Schedule your showing today!
